headline: Sysco to Report Q1 Earnings: Should You Expect a Beat This Time?
summary: SYY's first-quarter earnings are likely to have shown growth, helped by digital tools and loyalty programs, but rising costs remain a headwind.

headline: Exploring Analyst Estimates for Sysco (SYY) Q1 Earnings, Beyond Revenue and EPS
